{"tid":261268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電話騙案】「假冒官員」案上升　逾半中招者30歲以下　警：少看新聞欠認知","createTime":"2017-05-28T10:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T19:46:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef3695896b95c29e08515494861d73a24b104bf","tid":261268,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170528/s00001/11ca0521fe47e79b903e5dce8338a340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F11ca0521fe47e79b903e5dce8338a340.jpg&h=de5aec49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話騙案無日無之，警方公布最新騙案數字，發現整體電話騙案雖然有下降，但當中「假冒官員」的電話騙案卻上升。東九龍刑事總區刑事總部偵緝總督察譚威信表示，「假冒官員」騙案的受害人有達56%為30歲以下的年輕人，估計與其忙於工作及學業，「比較少看新聞」，對電話騙案乏認知有關。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方數字，今年首4個月整體共有279宗電話騙案，較去年同期少2宗，當中217宗招致損失，涉及金額為8490萬元。騙案中，有182宗為「假冒官員」類，佔整體的65%，亦較去年同期上升28宗；當中有156宗最終招致損失，達共8053萬元。<br />\n<br />\n譚威信提醒，詐騙電話多來自內地或海外，其來電顯示亦多以「+852」作頭，呼籲市民多加留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00001/1495964573894?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F1495964573894%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=7iP2ZoPNriUAOaJDGUziEFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=cfce7074\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170528%2Fs00001%2F1495964573894%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=aee3b325\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170528/s00001/1495964573894?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"e896971d14d8a72f7220eb9b4611ed140299a612","tid":261268,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"中既都係支那人 怕咩"},{"pid":"a12b36f135d81055b1b6e6dd0f6c62ca75838a30","tid":261268,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd